This is GUI for dictionary tryout written in wxpython.
Tested with buzhug with 3 words गरिब, सुर्य, आँखा

Requirement wxpython,buzhug
In ubuntu 
sudo apt-get install wxversion python-buzhug

Run main.py

Its the clone for  http://collaborate.d2labs.org/projects/shabdartha/

tested in Ubuntu and Fedora

Those who can contribute to this project especially in database building sector are welcome.
